# prettier ignore — keep symmetrical with the relevant lines in .gitignore
# (build outputs, package-manager state, lockfiles). Rust files are
# formatted by rustfmt via `cargo fmt`; markdown is left alone because
# prettier reflows it in ways that hurt readability of long-form docs.

**/node_modules/
**/.svelte-kit/
**/build/
**/dist/
**/.bun/
**/target/

# Lockfiles — never reformat
bun.lock
Cargo.lock
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

# Docs are hand-curated long-form prose
docs/
README.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
CODE_OF_ETHICS.md

# Rust source
**/*.rs

# Generated artefacts
**/*.generated.*
apps/web-ui/tokens/tokens.css
